name: Soulblazer: Fietena
description: A character standee inspired by Fietena, the fierce lead of the popular comic The Soulblazer Saga. Her striking pose captures both her fearless spirit and unshakable passion for battle.\n"There's no backing out now. Let's do this!"\nOf course, charging in together doesn't always lead to a perfect victory. Even so, the passion you shared and the effort you gave were real. And maybe someday, all of it will grow into something brilliant, something you can look back on without regrets.
